window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>An old classic from a Hugo Award Winning author.&nbsp;</p> <p>With an introductory biography of the late Isaac Asimov, this classic work gets better.</p> <p>Red and Slim found the two strange little animals the morning after they heard the thunder sounds. They knew that they could never show their new pets to their parents. Enjoy the listen, leave a review and check out our other retro sci-fi books!</p>"; 
